name: Eternal Sunrise (Still version)
description:
This is the original photo that inspired the 1:1 moving artwork and song "Eternal Sunrise" on my foundation profile.

The original photo was taken from the top of Bishop's Peak in San Luis Obispo California. Thank you to my adventure partners/photo subjects Henry and Sammy-Jo for waking up at 4am to hike up this mountain with me to get the shot!

To see the 1:1 piece head to: https://foundation.app/@patricklawler
